WEBVTT

00:09.905 --> 00:12.708
Previously on "Mr. Mercedes"...

00:12.408 --> 00:14.277
Have any cobwebs you just can't shake?

00:14.477 --> 00:17.313
This is mine.
I want to know.

00:17.513 --> 00:19.549
I want to know who tormented my sister.

00:21.217 --> 00:23.653
You're a goddamn dead man.

00:23.853 --> 00:27.190
You smell like a saloon,
loaded man, loaded gun.

00:27.390 --> 00:28.574
It's not good, Bill.

00:28.774 --> 00:29.759
You almost shot a kid.

00:29.959 --> 00:31.427
How much have you been drinking lately?

00:31.627 --> 00:32.395
Not enough.

00:32.595 --> 00:34.564
I don't want to go
to your funeral in 6 months.

00:35.865 --> 00:37.434
What does it do?

00:37.634 --> 00:40.503
Let's just say it activates

00:40.703 --> 00:42.955
and deactivates almost anything I want.

00:43.155 --> 00:45.408
Brady, my deeper concern runs to you.

00:45.608 --> 00:46.443
You're weird.

00:46.643 --> 00:48.912
Sometimes you come across
as just plain weird.

00:52.115 --> 00:53.650
Oh, Jesus! God!

00:53.850 --> 00:56.920
Got a letter from my new pen pal,
put this one in writing.

00:57.120 --> 00:57.987
"Care to get in touch?

00:58.187 --> 00:59.989
Try Under Debbie's Blue Umbrella."

